sentences: In 2005, he won the Best Supporting Actor award for his portrayal of Zhou Daqiu, the antagonist, in Portrait of Home.
The character was also voted the Top 10 Most Memorable Villains at the Star Awards 2007 anniversary special.
He married Serena Yeo in December 2009, and they have a son Kayden (2011) and a daughter Bethany (2013).
